The TimeLife Treasury of Christmas is a mail order Christmas music collection produced by TimeLife Music in cooperation with RCA/Ariola International. It was first available in 1986, and contained 45 songs on three LP records, two cassettes or two compact discs. Record One, Side One Record One, Side Two Record Two, Side Three Record Two, Side Four Record Three, Side Five Record Three, Side Six In 2002, TimeLife Music and BMG Special Products produced an updated version of The TimeLife Treasury of Christmas featuring a slightly different program of songs. This version contains 43 songs on two compact discs. Disc One Disc Two
